                <h1>Where Is Rice University Located?</h1>
                <p>Rice University is located in Houston, Texas, USA. Established in 1912, this prestigious private research university sits within the Museum District, near the Texas Medical Center. The campus features stunning architecture and beautiful green spaces, providing an ideal environment for learning and research.</p>
